      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Types of objects in Database.\nData Types\nColoumn Data Constraints/Data Constraints\nCatogories in SQL\n    - Data Defination Language DDL\n    - Data Manipulation Language DML\n    - Transaction Control Language TCL\n    - Data Control Lanugage DCL\n    - Data Retrieval Language DRL\nACID in Database.\nTransaction in Database.\nATOMIC transactions in Database.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Types of objects in Database.\nData Types\nColoumn Data Constraints/Data Constraints\nCatogories in SQL\n    - Data Defination Language DDL\n    - Data Manipulation Language DML\n    - Transaction Control Language TCL\n    - Data Control Lanugage DCL\n    - Data Retrieval Language DRL\nACID in Database.\nTransaction in Database.\nATOMIC transactions in Database.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
