      "updated": 1782761761417,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.CHAR         EX: lets say we defined a col with CHAR5, Full space req for 5chars is consumed in memory even tough we store only 3lets word  \n2.VARCHAR    Ex: only reqired space is consumed eventough, not like CHAR\n3.INTEGER/NUMBER   know the difference between decimal and integer\n4.DECIMAL    ||\n5.DATE         DD-MON-YYYY\n6.TIMESTAMP DD-MON-YYYY HH:MM:SS:SSSSSS\n7.CLOB    Character Large Object --> Resume     \n8.BLOB    Binary Large Object --> Photo\n9.BFILE   Audio or Video file.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.CHAR         EX: lets say we defined a col with CHAR5, Full space req for 5chars is consumed in memory even tough we store only 3lets word  \n2.VARCHAR    Ex: only reqired space is consumed eventough, not like CHAR\n3.INTEGER/NUMBER   know the difference between decimal and integer\n4.DECIMAL    ||\n5.DATE         DD-MON-YYYY\n6.TIMESTAMP DD-MON-YYYY HH:MM:SS:SSSSSS\n7.CLOB    Character Large Object --> Resume     \n8.BLOB    Binary Large Object --> Photo\n9.BFILE   Audio or Video file.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
