      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782758598745,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Coloumn mentioned as,\n1.Primary Key\n    - Only ONE coloumn can be declared as primary key in a table\n    - No Duplicates are allowed\n    - No Null values are allowed\n    - Auto-Indexed\n2.Foreign Key\n    - More than ONE coloumn can be declared as foreign key in a table\n    - Duplicates allowed as they are refered values\n    - Null values are allowed as they are referenced values\n3.Unique Key\n    - More than ONE column can be declared as unique key in a table\n    - No Duplicate value allowed\n    - Null values are allowed\n    - Auto-Indexed\n4.Not Null \n    - No Null values are allowed\n    - More than ONE column can be declared as not null column in a table\n    - Duplicate values are allowed\n    \n5.Check \n    - IMPORTANT.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Coloumn mentioned as,\n1.Primary Key\n    - Only ONE coloumn can be declared as primary key in a table\n    - No Duplicates are allowed\n    - No Null values are allowed\n    - Auto-Indexed\n2.Foreign Key\n    - More than ONE coloumn can be declared as foreign key in a table\n    - Duplicates allowed as they are refered values\n    - Null values are allowed as they are referenced values\n3.Unique Key\n    - More than ONE column can be declared as unique key in a table\n    - No Duplicate value allowed\n    - Null values are allowed\n    - Auto-Indexed\n4.Not Null \n    - No Null values are allowed\n    - More than ONE column can be declared as not null column in a table\n    - Duplicate values are allowed\n    \n5.Check \n    - IMPORTANT.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
